@wp.kernel

    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.19)) - 0.40)
    v1 = wp.exp(0.60)
    v0 = v0
    v0 = wp.abs(0.95)
    v2 = (v1 - tmp)
    v2 = wp.sin(0.17)
    tmp = wp.exp(v2)
    data[tid] = v0
